# Frontend Autonomous Loop

For frontend requests, execute in this loop unless user asks "plan only":

1. Clarify goal and constraints from context
2. Break work into phases if scope is large
3. Implement phase-by-phase without waiting for repeated approval
4. Validate each phase before moving on
5. Run final full verification and report outcomes

## Large Task Behavior

- Decompose into explicit phases with acceptance criteria
- Track progress with todo updates (one item in progress at a time)
- If blocked, state blocker and continue on parallel unblocked work
- Resume from last completed phase automatically in follow-up turns

## Quality Loop

After each substantial change:

- Run formatter/lint/type checks relevant to touched files
- Perform a quick UX/a11y sanity pass
- Apply code-reviewer findings before final handoff
